nodes.text: This rebel was a Human female from Onderon who served the Onderon rebels during the Clone Wars.

When Onderons's king sided with the Confederacy of Independent Systems, this rebel fought to gain back its freedom. During within the battle, the rebel was stationed at The nest when the base was attacked by an HMP and several droids. The rebel was approached by a BX-series droid commando who demanded the location of the king but the rebel refused to tell, and was subsequently shot in the head.
The rebel was voiced by Catherine Taber, who also voices Senator Padmé Amidala in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series.
